# Templates Directory

This directory contains Handlebars templates for code generation.

## Available Templates

- **entity.hbs** - TypeORM entity with TypeGraphQL decorators
- **resolver.hbs** - GraphQL resolver with CRUD operations
- **job.hbs** - Background job class
- **migration.hbs** - Database migration
- **policy.hbs** - Authorization policy
- **service.hbs** - Service class

## Template Variables

Templates have access to Handlebars helpers:
- `{{pascalCase name}}` - PascalCase conversion
- `{{camelCase name}}` - camelCase conversion
- `{{kebabCase name}}` - kebab-case conversion
- `{{snakeCase name}}` - snake_case conversion
- `{{pluralize name}}` - Pluralization
- `{{singularize name}}` - Singularization
- `{{timestamp}}` - Current ISO timestamp
- `{{year}}` - Current year
